Company Overview of ARAMARK Food and Support Services Group, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
ARAMARK Food and Support Services Group, Inc. provides food services, refreshment, facility and other support services, for businesses, healthcare facilities, school districts, colleges and universities, conference and convention centers, national and state parks, sports, entertainment and recreational venues and correctional institutions. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is based in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. ARAMARK Food and Support Services Group, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of ARAMARK Corporation.


1101 Market StreetPhiladelphia, PA 19107United StatesFounded in 1989



Phone: 215-238-3000

Fax: 215-238-3333








